keyFacts: A meeting titled 'Epstein Trust Discussion' was scheduled for July 6, 2020, by the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS).
The meeting was conducted via WebEx, indicating remote coordination among legal personnel.
The document shows ongoing legal administrative work related to the Epstein case trust in mid-2020.
All participant names are redacted or referred to by organizational role (USANYS Contractor).
The meeting was scheduled for 45 minutes (1:15 PM to 2:00 PM Eastern Time).
